411
00:24:47,230 --> 00:24:49,070
It is not always true.

412
00:24:49,070 --> 00:24:52,310
In fact, we could
make a simple example

413
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:53,935
to see why that's
not always the case.

414
00:25:07,191 --> 00:25:07,690
All right.

