988
00:57:07,740 --> 00:57:15,250
And the proof, question
mark, is you let Ai

989
00:57:15,250 --> 00:57:25,220
be the event that the i-th die
comes up N. And i is 1 to 3

990
00:57:25,220 --> 00:57:26,867
